OL,4,CMartin Bashir: BBC religion editor
OL,5,Cleaves the corporation
OL,6, Martin Bashir has stepped down from his
OL,7, role as the BBC's religion editor, the
OL,8, corporation has confirmed.
OL,10,FBashir, 58, has reported on religious
OL,11,Faffairs for the BBC since 2016, and
OL,12,Fpreviously worked for programmes
OL,13,Fincluding Panorama.
OL,15,FThe corporation said he was leaving due
OL,16,Fto ongoing health issues.
OL,18,FHis departure comes after questions
OL,19,Fwere raised about how he secured an
OL,20,Finterview with Princess Diana for
OL,21,FPanorama in 1995.
